    "content" : "Hi all.\n<br> \n<br> Recently fitted a CE 4 inch narrowed beam and I was wondering if anybody had managed to fit an anti roll bar to one?? \n<br> CE say you don't need one and it would actually make it worse??? Having driven splities for years I would say it's a much needed part of the suspension set up?\n<br> \n<br> Any thoughts, solutions or opinions are gratefully received. \n<br> \n<br> Cheers\n<br> Rob",
